{"type": "article", "id": 2220, "title": "Nooka 计时手表", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:53:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222256m1aTVhcjCMER6kAp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">时尚品牌 Nooka 日前推出了他们的首款计时手表 Nookrono ，集摩登、简约与纯净风格于一身。Nooka 这次既没有选用瑞士手表机芯也没有选用日本手表机芯，而是动用自家的工程师完成了 Nookrono 的全部制作工艺。目前，Nookrono 正在</span><a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/nookrono-chronograph-watches-by-nooka\" target=\"_blank\">Indiegogo</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> 上进行众筹，预计将于 12 月正式发售。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135059Yg5uq8iNFldpAKvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135100yH4PuKiGexsj60Vr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135101k4byDfYK31tLGvJM.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}